LEGISLATURE OF NEBRASKA
ONE HUNDRED NINTH LEGISLATURE
SECOND SESSION
LEGISLATIVE BILL 429
FINAL READING
Introduced by Murman, 38; Ballard, 21; Clements, 2; DeKay, 40; Hansen,
16; Holdcroft, 36; Ibach, 44; Jacobson, 42; Kauth, 31;
Lippincott, 34; Lonowski, 33; Sanders, 45; Sorrentino, 39;
